      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents a superb mechanical example of the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 era. Featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline, the powertrain delivers linear thrust through a precise 6-speed manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis retains its factory-intended kinematics with a multi-link rear setup and stiffened subframe bushings. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including throttle actuator replacement and a comprehensive cooling system pressure test. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain integrity and lateral grip remain sharp, making it an ideal candidate for the discerning driver who prioritizes longitudinal performance and atmospheric induction over showroom-floor perfection.",
